			<div class="content" id="post-content-2382107">
									

<p>This is a collaboration between <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ladykatie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2150500); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2150500&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1443320022" alt="LadyKatie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2150500)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ladykatie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2150500); return false;">LadyKatie</a></span> and myself. It's been a while in coming, and it's a starting point for the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-1264304/new-canon-idea:on-mount-golgotha" target="_blank">On Mount Golgotha</a> canon.</p>
<p>So, where did <a href="/scp-012">SCP-012</a> come from? What does it mean? Why does it exist? We're going to explore and find out.</p>

