			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2383408">
									

<p>See, the concerns that Kalinin's raised here about 012 being a, let's not kid ourselves, bad article, and also being the premise of a major project is the main reason I've ignored the thread regarding this project, and why it took some effort on my part to start reading this. That being said, I liked this far more than I like 012 and <em>wish</em> that this didn't secure 012's place on the wiki more tightly. However, I'm approaching these stories with an open mind; if I dislike what I see, I'm going to downvote. I actually did like this and voted accordingly, but I really hope something more than just Lovecraftian descents into madness come out of this project.</p>

